sections.Trivia:
- In the TV guide magazine from May 2021, the episodes were titled The Inherited Revenge (引き継がれた復讐 ,Hikitsugareta Fukushū?)[1].
- Otosaka's SUV is a blue Nissan X-Trail, second generation. The license plate is 奥穂 330, ひ 74-63 (Okuho 330, hi 74-63).
- The car parked next to Otosaka's SUV is a white Nissan Elgrand, second generation.
- The car Kogoro falls on is a black Nissan Sylphy. The license plate is 新宿 300, さ 52-38 (Shinjuku 300, sa 52-38).
- Kogoro's rental car is a white Toyota Crown, thirteenth generation. The license plate is 新宿 300, わ 2-25 (Shinjuku 300, wa 2-25).
- The convenience store RANSUN is a knock-off of the famous Lawson retail chain.
- The sub-characters' surnames are related to each other, in which the first character of its kanji makes up for the following sets:
The four seasons (春, 夏, 秋, 冬)
Junpei Haruyama (春山 淳兵) represents spring (春);
Yoji Natsukawa (夏川 洋二) represents summer (夏);
Miyako Akiba (秋葉 都) represents autumn (秋);
Ryuzaburo Fuyuki (冬木 隆三郎) represents winter (冬).
The order of things (甲, 乙)
Takashi Komoto (甲本 高士) represents party A (甲);
Jinichi Otosaka (乙坂 仁一) represents party B (乙).
Orientations (上, 下)
Mr. Ueda and Mrs. Ueda (上田) represent up (上);
Mr. Shimoda and Mrs. Shimoda (下田) represent down (下).
